      "value": "<p>When an ally is hit by a weapon attack while within 10 feet of you, you can use your reaction and expend a use of your Channel the Force to attempt to divert the attack. When you do so, the damage the chosen ally takes from the attack is reduced by [[/r 1d10]] + your Wisdom or Charisma modifier (your choice) + your guardian level.</p>\n<p>At 11th level, the chosen ally must be within 30 feet of you to benefit from this feature. At 17th level, the chosen ally must be within 60 feet.</p>",
